LAUAAFBO.png" data-type="png" data-w="662" style="vertical-align: middle;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;" src="https://2-im.guokr.com/-PDQYP59vK8EZAh3oM8hQRW15z88KGeOn5waEkKGimiWAgAALAUAAFBO.png?imageView2/1/w/555/h/1110"></section></section><section powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="white-space: normal;"><br></p><p style="white-space: normal;">这些，将为促进我国海洋生态文明的建设，提升全社会海洋环保意识助力。</p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br></p><p style="white-space: normal;">OC实验室为所有人搭建起一扇扇面朝大海的窗，将最真实的海近距离展现在人们眼前。</p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br></p><p style="white-space: normal;">透过这些窗口，你可以随时随地关注中国的海洋的变化，分享每日见闻，并加入到海洋生态守护的行列中。</p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(15, 97, 164);">自此，“保护海洋”不再是遥远的口号，而是触手可及的日常。</span></strong></p></section><section powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="white-space: normal;"><br></p></section><section powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="white-space: normal;"><br></p></section><section style="text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;"><img data-ratio="0.06521739130434782" data-src="https://1-im.guokr.com/upR_Oqgt3rB9KgryapQ9wNIKMY2xQ0slp-y3c6GZCquyAgAALQAAAFBO.png" data-type="png" data-w="690" style="vertical-align: middle;box-sizing: border-box;" src="https://1-im.guokr.com/upR_Oqgt3rB9KgryapQ9wNIKMY2xQ0slp-y3c6GZCquyAgAALQAAAFBO.png?imageView2/1/w/555/h/36"></section></section><section style="font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);line-height: 1.5;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="white-space: normal;">作者：爱看海的小玉</p><p style="white-space: normal;">排版：雷昱儿</p><p style="white-space: normal;">题图来源：Pixabay</p></section><section powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="white-space: normal;"><br></p></section><section style="text-align: center;color: rgb(15, 97, 164);" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p><strong>欢迎个人转发到朋友圈</strong></p></section><section style="text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-b